<%= render "shared/navbar" %>
<main>
  <header class="w-full h-screen-2/3 bg-errorhead bg-cover bg-center flex justify-center items-center">
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center mx-20 opacity-0 duration-[1000ms] scale-x-0"
      x-intersect="$el.classList.add('opacity-100', 'scale-x-100', 'z-0')"
      >
        <h1 class=" text-center text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold">
          Become an Owner/Operator<br>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-center text-xl py-3 font-semibold">
        Make money by partnering with 99 Lawn Care
        </p>
        <%= link_to 'Send a Message', contact_path, class: "text-center block p-3 px-6 bg-lime-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-lime-300 " %>
      </div>
  </header>
</main>

<section class="flex flex-col items-center pb-10">
    <div class="w-4/5 lg:w-3/5 pt-10 flex flex-col items-center">
      <!--Desktop-->
      <h1 class="font-bold text-center text-3xl hidden lg:block">
        Discover why becoming an Owner Operator <br>is a great business opportunity 
      </h1>
      <!--Mobile-->
      <h1 class="font-bold text-center text-3xl lg:hidden">
        Become an<br> Owner Operator
      </h1>
      <p class="text-2xl py-10 lg:w-3/5 w-4/5 text-center">
        By partnering with 99 Lawn Care, you're entering into a turnkey business that has already been proven successful. 
      </p>
      <p class="font-semibold pb-10 text-xl lg:w-3/5 w-4/5 text-center">
        We provide the training and resources to get your company off the ground and running smoothly.  We offer the benefit of economies of scale. 
      </p>

      <p class="font-regular text-lg lg:w-3/5 w-4/5 text-center">
        You can leverage the power of the 99 Lawn Care network and get better deals on supplies and equipment; help in finding new customers and leads; training and support so you become successful.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-100 py-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row lg:justify-center lg:items-center lg:px-5">

        <div class="lg:w-2/5 mx-5">
          <h3 class="text-lime-700 text-4xl font-semibold py-5 text-center" style="">
            1. Low Start Up Costs
          </h3>
          
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-2/5 flex flex-col items-center">
        <%= image_tag "moneyball.webp", alt: "ball of money", class: "lg:rounded-xl lg:w-3/5" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:justify-center">
        <div class="lg:w-4/5 mx-5 lg:px-5">
          <p class="text-slate-900 text-lg py-5">
            One of the main advantages of becoming a lawn care owner/operator is that it generally has relatively low startup costs compared to other types of businesses. This can make it an attractive option for entrepreneurs who are looking to start a business. Starting a lawn care business starts with purchasing equipment, such as lawn mowers, edgers, and leaf blowers. These costs can typically be kept relatively low if you are careful about what you invest in. 99 Lawn Care will help you find good deals on equipment.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row-reverse lg:justify-center lg:items-center">

        <div class="lg:w-2/5 mx-5">
          <h3 class="text-lime-700 text-4xl font-semibold py-5 text-center" style="">
            2. High Demand
          </h3>
          
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-2/5 flex flex-col items-center">
          <%= image_tag "smilewoman.webp", alt: "Woman mowing grass", class: "lg:rounded-xl lg:w-3/4" %>
          <div class="text-sm italic text-slate-500 pt-2">Anyone can be an owner operator</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:justify-center">
        <div class="lg:w-4/5 mx-5 lg:px-5">
          <p class="text-slate-900 text-lg py-5">
            Lawn care is a service that is always in demand. People are always looking for ways to maintain their lawns and keep them looking attractive. But many people are busy with work and other commitments and may not have the time to take care of their own lawns. This creates an opportunity for lawn care businesses to provide a valuable service.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row lg:justify-center lg:items-center">

        <div class="lg:w-2/5 mx-5">
          <h3 class="text-lime-700 text-4xl font-semibold py-5 text-center" style="">
            3. Flexibility
          </h3>
          
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-2/5 flex flex-col items-center">
          <%= image_tag "flexibility.webp", alt: "Woman mowing grass", class: "lg:rounded-xl lg:w-4/5" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:justify-center">
        <div class="lg:w-4/5 mx-5 lg:px-5">
          <p class="text-slate-900 text-lg py-5">
            Owning a lawn care businesses can also be flexible in terms of the services you offer and the hours you work, which makes becoming an owner operator for a lawn care business a good option for those looking for a business that fits their schedule.  You can set your own hours and work as much or as little as you want, depending on your schedule and workload.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
<%= render "shared/footer" %>